{
  "id": "adv_card_mei_12_01_short",
  "title": "早坂芽衣 (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_outside-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "もう九月かぁ……\n夏休みは終わったけど、まだまだ暑いよね",
      "startTime": 3.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "こんな暑い日はばしゃーんって水に飛び込みたくなるよ\n冷たくて気持ちいいだろうな～",
      "startTime": 12.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "夏の涼み方までアクティブなのは芽衣らしいな\n芽衣は暑さで気が滅入ったりしないのか？",
      "startTime": 19.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "むしろ、照りつける太陽を見たら\n「夏だー！」って感じで元気がわいてくるかな？",
      "startTime": 26.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "あと、桜が咲いてるのを見たら\n「春だー！」って元気になるし",
      "startTime": 33.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "落ち葉を見たら「秋だー！」って元気になるし\n雪を見たら「冬だー！」って元気になるよね！",
      "startTime": 39.9666674297,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "年中元気で羨ましいよ\n芽衣は夏バテなんてしなさそうだな",
      "startTime": 47.2333340963,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "そうだね～。今年は海で合宿したり、ミクちゃんの\nライブに出演したり、すっごく充実してたでしょ？",
      "startTime": 54.7333340963,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "おかげで毎日楽しくて\n夏の疲れも全部吹き飛んじゃった",
      "startTime": 60.433335368,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_12_01-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "あ、でも、この夏でひとつだけ心残りがあるかも……",
      "startTime": 63.643832366,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}